text: Julia Chevanne-Gimel (born 7 November 1975) is a French equestrian. She competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics. She became the French national champion in 2003 and 2007. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:French female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Paris
